title: Moe Was Rude And Now She Hates Him! Here's His Apology.
description:
Covid-19 has forced a lot of us into a routine of being used to being alone, especially in the workplace. We’ve become accustomed to there only being a handful of people around, so this week, when more people began coming back into the office, things got a little weird.
For Moe in particular.
